---
import Base from '../../layouts/Base.astro'
import RedditFeed from '../../components/RedditFeed.astro'
import livePosts from '../../data/reddit-seed/live.json'
---

<Base
  title="Living in Bermuda — Residents Guide"
  description="For people who call Bermuda home: local events, deals, the directory, and the things you discover after the first six months."
>
  <section class="hero" style="padding-block: var(--space-16);">
    <div class="hero__inner">
      <nav aria-label="Breadcrumb">
        <ol class="breadcrumb" style="justify-content: center; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.6);">
          <li><a href="/" style="color: rgba(255,255,255,0.6);">Home</a></li>
          <li class="breadcrumb__sep" aria-hidden="true">›</li>
          <li style="color: rgba(255,255,255,0.9);">Living</li>
        </ol>
      </nav>
      <h1 class="hero-title">Living in Bermuda</h1>
      <p class="hero-subtitle">
        For people who call it home.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <div class="container" style="padding-block: var(--space-12);">

    <div style="background-color: var(--color-amber-muted); border: 1px solid var(--color-amber); border-radius: var(--radius-lg); padding: var(--space-8); margin-bottom: var(--space-10);">
      <h2 style="font-size: var(--text-xl); margin-bottom: var(--space-3);">This section is growing</h2>
      <p style="color: var(--color-ink); margin-bottom: var(--space-2);">
        The residents section launches with the directory and key links.
        Events and local deals are Phase 2 — they require regular curation that comes after
        the foundation is solid.
      </p>
      <p style="color: var(--color-muted); font-size: var(--text-sm); margin: 0;">
        Notable gap: nothingtodoinbermuda.com (the go-to local events calendar) was absorbed
        into the Bermuda Tourism Authority portal. A genuine community events digest is an
        unmet need. Coming in Phase 2.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="card-grid card-grid-3">
      <!-- Directory -->
      <a href="/directory" class="link-card link-card--featured">
        <p class="link-card__eyebrow">Directory</p>
        <h3 class="link-card__title">Browse Local Businesses</h3>
        <p class="link-card__desc">
          Restaurants, schools, insurers, real estate, events — filtered for residents.
          The directory includes businesses relevant to daily life, not just tourist needs.
        </p>
        <p style="margin-top: var(--space-4); font-size: var(--text-sm); color: var(--color-ocean); font-weight: 600;">
          Browse directory →
        </p>
      </a>

      <!-- Events placeholder -->
      <div class="link-card" style="opacity: 0.6; cursor: default;">
        <p class="link-card__eyebrow">Coming in Phase 2</p>
        <h3 class="link-card__title">Events Calendar</h3>
        <p class="link-card__desc">
          Local events, community notices, Bermuda Heroes Weekend, Restaurant Week,
          Cup Match — curated so you don't miss them.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Deals placeholder -->
      <div class="link-card" style="opacity: 0.6; cursor: default;">
        <p class="link-card__eyebrow">Coming in Phase 2</p>
        <h3 class="link-card__title">Local Deals</h3>
        <p class="link-card__desc">
          Restaurant Week prix-fixe offers, accommodation deals, seasonal promotions
          from directory partners. A genuine gap nobody is filling well right now.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- For movers who just arrived -->
    <section style="margin-top: var(--space-12); padding: var(--space-8); background-color: var(--color-sand); border-radius: var(--radius-lg);">
      <h2 style="font-size: var(--text-2xl); margin-bottom: var(--space-4);">New to Bermuda? Start with these</h2>
      <ul class="prose" style="padding-left: var(--space-6); max-width: 640px;">
        <li style="margin-bottom: var(--space-3);">
          <a href="/move/tools/assessment-number">The one-car-per-household rule</a> —
          understand this before you try to bring a car over.
        </li>
        <li style="margin-bottom: var(--space-3);">
          <a href="/directory?filter=insurance">Mandatory health insurance</a> —
          you need SHB coverage from day one. Argus Group and BF&M are the main providers.
        </li>
        <li style="margin-bottom: var(--space-3);">
          <a href="/directory?filter=education">Schools</a> —
          Saltus, Bermuda High School, Warwick Academy, The Bermuda Institute.
          Apply early — competitive year groups fill fast.
        </li>
        <li style="margin-bottom: var(--space-3);">
          <a href="https://www.table.bm" rel="noopener" target="_blank">Table.bm</a> —
          the best way to discover restaurants and catch Restaurant Week.
        </li>
      </ul>
    </section>

  </div>

  <RedditFeed posts={livePosts} />
</Base>
